videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe strikes first
videos.description: Caleb Evans finds RJ Turner on a wide receiver screen for a 21-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe recovers fumble in Appalachian State territory
videos.description: LaMon David Griffith jumps on the loose football after Daetrich Harrington fumbles in his own territory.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe scores on possession after turnover
videos.description: Caleb Evans throws a 39-yard strike to Marcus Green to give the Warhawks a two-touchdown lead.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe returns kickoff 95 yards for TD
videos.description: Marcus Green dodges defenders and runs untouched for a 95-yard kickoff return.

videos.headline: Lamb puts Appalachian State in the red zone
videos.description: Taylor Lamb rushes for 28 yards on a quarterback keeper to put the Mountaineers at Louisiana Monroe's 12-yard line.

videos.headline: Appalachian State scores first TD
videos.description: Taylor Lamb finds Ike Lewis in the corner of the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown to close the gap to 21-10.

videos.headline: Lamb and Lewis connect for second TD
videos.description: Appalachian State's Taylor Lamb throws a perfect ball to Ike Lewis for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Appalachian State's Moore burst for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Taylor Lamb throws a short pass to Jalin Moore, who breaks free for a 75-yard touchdown to bring the Mountaineers within 28-24.
